<subSubSection lastPageId="2" lastPageNumber="255" pageId="1" pageNumber="254" type="key">
<keyStep pageId="1" pageNumber="254">
<paragraph blockId="1.[151,1437,1624,2027]" pageId="1" pageNumber="254">
<keyLead pageId="1" pageNumber="254">
1. Hypandrium of three sclerites, two small, elongate side sclerites flanking a large, central sclerite (see 
<figureCitation box="[1207,1276,1624,1646]" captionStart="FIGURES 1–10" captionStartId="4.[151,264,1921,1945]" captionTargetBox="[159,1431,193,1889]" captionTargetId="figure-25@4.[151,1435,181,1897]" captionTargetPageId="4" captionText="FIGURES 1–10. Loneura cavernicola sp. nov. (Holotype male). 1. Front view of head. 2. Lacinial tip. 3. Antennae. 4. Left forewing. 5. Left hindwing. 6. Right forewing. 7. Right hindwing. 8. Fore- leg. 9. Mid- leg 10. Hind- leg. Scales in mm." figureDoi="http://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.6831837" httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/6831837/files/figure.png" pageId="1" pageNumber="254">
Fig. 
<quantity box="[1252,1276,1624,1645]" metricMagnitude="-1" metricUnit="m" metricValue="2.54" pageId="1" pageNumber="254" unit="in" value="10.0">10</quantity>
</figureCitation>
in 
<bibRefCitation author="Cutrim, M. &amp; Silva-Neto, A. M. &amp; Garcia Aldrete, A. N. &amp; Rafael, J. A." pageId="1" pageNumber="254" pagination="487 - 502" refId="ref9457" refString="Cutrim, M., Silva-Neto, A. M., Garcia Aldrete, A. N. &amp; Rafael, J. A. (2021 b) Identification key, checklist and new species of Loneura Navas (Psocodea: ' Psocoptera': Ptiloneuridae) from Brazil. Zootaxa, 5057 (4), 487 - 502. https: // doi. org / 10.11646 / zootaxa. 5057.4.2" type="journal article" year="2021">
Cutrim 
<emphasis box="[1382,1431,1624,1645]" italics="true" pageId="1" pageNumber="254">et al.</emphasis>
, 2021b
</bibRefCitation>
).............................................................................. 
<taxonomicName box="[1243,1324,1654,1675]" class="Insecta" family="Ptiloneuridae" genus="Loneura" kingdom="Animalia" order="Psocodea" pageId="1" pageNumber="254" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis box="[1243,1324,1654,1675]" italics="true" pageId="1" pageNumber="254">Loneura</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
group I....2
</keyLead>
</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="1.[151,1437,1624,2027]" pageId="1" pageNumber="254">
<keyLead pageId="1" pageNumber="254">
- Hypandrium of one sclerite, resulting from the fusion of the proximal ends of the side sclerites to the central sclerite, this extended mesally on each side, with two posterior processes in the middle, variously shaped (see 
<figureCitation box="[1197,1268,1712,1734]" captionStart="FIGURES 27–32" captionStartId="7.[151,264,1943,1967]" captionTargetBox="[188,1405,188,1909]" captionTargetId="figure-19@7.[178,1409,181,1919]" captionTargetPageId="7" captionText="FIGURES 27–32. Loneura cavernicola sp. nov. (Paratype female). 27. Ninth sternum and gonapophyses (image). 28. Ninth sternum and gonapophyses (drawing). 29. Subgenital plate (image). 30. Subgenital plate (drawing). 31. Left paraproct and epiproct (image). 32. Left paraproct and epiproct (drawing). Scales in mm." figureDoi="http://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.6831845" httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/6831845/files/figure.png" pageId="1" pageNumber="254">
Fig. 
<quantity box="[1244,1268,1712,1733]" metricMagnitude="-1" metricUnit="m" metricValue="7.366" pageId="1" pageNumber="254" unit="in" value="29.0">29</quantity>
</figureCitation>
in 
<bibRefCitation author="Cutrim, M. &amp; Silva-Neto, A. M. &amp; Garcia Aldrete, A. N. &amp; Rafael, J. A." pageId="1" pageNumber="254" pagination="487 - 502" refId="ref9457" refString="Cutrim, M., Silva-Neto, A. M., Garcia Aldrete, A. N. &amp; Rafael, J. A. (2021 b) Identification key, checklist and new species of Loneura Navas (Psocodea: ' Psocoptera': Ptiloneuridae) from Brazil. Zootaxa, 5057 (4), 487 - 502. https: // doi. org / 10.11646 / zootaxa. 5057.4.2" type="journal article" year="2021">
Cutrim 
<emphasis box="[1380,1431,1712,1733]" italics="true" pageId="1" pageNumber="254">et al.</emphasis>
, 2021b
</bibRefCitation>
)............................................................................... 
<taxonomicName box="[1241,1322,1742,1763]" class="Insecta" family="Ptiloneuridae" genus="Loneura" kingdom="Animalia" order="Psocodea" pageId="1" pageNumber="254" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis box="[1241,1322,1742,1763]" italics="true" pageId="1" pageNumber="254">Loneura</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
group II...3
</keyLead>
</paragraph>
</keyStep>
<keyStep pageId="1" pageNumber="254">
<paragraph blockId="1.[151,1437,1624,2027]" pageId="1" pageNumber="254">
<keyLead pageId="1" pageNumber="254">
2. Central sclerite of the hypandrium with one posterior projection, distally bifurcated, with a postero-lateral connection joining the central and lateral sclerites (see 
<figureCitation box="[568,636,1800,1822]" captionStart="FIGURES 1–10" captionStartId="4.[151,264,1921,1945]" captionTargetBox="[159,1431,193,1889]" captionTargetId="figure-25@4.[151,1435,181,1897]" captionTargetPageId="4" captionText="FIGURES 1–10. Loneura cavernicola sp. nov. (Holotype male). 1. Front view of head. 2. Lacinial tip. 3. Antennae. 4. Left forewing. 5. Left hindwing. 6. Right forewing. 7. Right hindwing. 8. Fore- leg. 9. Mid- leg 10. Hind- leg. Scales in mm." figureDoi="http://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.6831837" httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/6831837/files/figure.png" pageId="1" pageNumber="254">
Fig. 
<quantity box="[612,636,1800,1821]" metricMagnitude="-1" metricUnit="m" metricValue="2.54" pageId="1" pageNumber="254" unit="in" value="10.0">10</quantity>
</figureCitation>
in 
<bibRefCitation author="Cutrim, M. &amp; Silva-Neto, A. M. &amp; Garcia Aldrete, A. N. &amp; Rafael, J. A." box="[667,862,1800,1822]" pageId="1" pageNumber="254" pagination="487 - 502" refId="ref9457" refString="Cutrim, M., Silva-Neto, A. M., Garcia Aldrete, A. N. &amp; Rafael, J. A. (2021 b) Identification key, checklist and new species of Loneura Navas (Psocodea: ' Psocoptera': Ptiloneuridae) from Brazil. Zootaxa, 5057 (4), 487 - 502. https: // doi. org / 10.11646 / zootaxa. 5057.4.2" type="journal article" year="2021">
Cutrim 
<emphasis box="[741,790,1800,1821]" italics="true" pageId="1" pageNumber="254">et al.</emphasis>
, 2021b
</bibRefCitation>
).......................... 
<taxonomicName authority="Cutrim et al." authorityName="Cutrim" box="[1184,1437,1800,1822]" class="Insecta" family="Ptiloneuridae" genus="Loneura" kingdom="Animalia" order="Psocodea" pageId="1" pageNumber="254" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="manauara">
<emphasis box="[1184,1309,1800,1821]" italics="true" pageId="1" pageNumber="254">L. manauara</emphasis>
