<emphasis box="[1388,1437,1800,1821]" italics="true" pageId="1" pageNumber="254">et al.</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
</keyLead>
</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="1.[151,1437,1624,2027]" box="[151,1436,1829,1851]" pageId="1" pageNumber="254">
<keyLead box="[151,1436,1829,1851]" pageId="1" pageNumber="254">- Hypandrium with more than one posterior projection......................................................... 4</keyLead>
</paragraph>
</keyStep>
<keyStep pageId="1" pageNumber="254">
<paragraph blockId="1.[151,1437,1624,2027]" pageId="1" pageNumber="254">
<keyLead pageId="1" pageNumber="254">
3. Posterior projections of the hypandrium near to each other, projected from the middle, distally curved outward, with deep median incision that reaches near the base (see 
<figureCitation box="[651,719,1888,1910]" captionStart="FIGURES 27–32" captionStartId="7.[151,264,1943,1967]" captionTargetBox="[188,1405,188,1909]" captionTargetId="figure-19@7.[178,1409,181,1919]" captionTargetPageId="7" captionText="FIGURES 27–32. Loneura cavernicola sp. nov. (Paratype female). 27. Ninth sternum and gonapophyses (image). 28. Ninth sternum and gonapophyses (drawing). 29. Subgenital plate (image). 30. Subgenital plate (drawing). 31. Left paraproct and epiproct (image). 32. Left paraproct and epiproct (drawing). Scales in mm." figureDoi="http://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.6831845" httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/6831845/files/figure.png" pageId="1" pageNumber="254">
Fig. 
<quantity box="[695,719,1888,1909]" metricMagnitude="-1" metricUnit="m" metricValue="7.366" pageId="1" pageNumber="254" unit="in" value="29.0">29</quantity>
</figureCitation>
in 
<bibRefCitation author="Cutrim, M. &amp; Silva-Neto, A. M. &amp; Garcia Aldrete, A. N. &amp; Rafael, J. A." box="[750,945,1888,1910]" pageId="1" pageNumber="254" pagination="487 - 502" refId="ref9457" refString="Cutrim, M., Silva-Neto, A. M., Garcia Aldrete, A. N. &amp; Rafael, J. A. (2021 b) Identification key, checklist and new species of Loneura Navas (Psocodea: ' Psocoptera': Ptiloneuridae) from Brazil. Zootaxa, 5057 (4), 487 - 502. https: // doi. org / 10.11646 / zootaxa. 5057.4.2" type="journal article" year="2021">
Cutrim 
<emphasis box="[824,873,1888,1909]" italics="true" pageId="1" pageNumber="254">et al.</emphasis>
, 2021b
</bibRefCitation>
)...................... 
<taxonomicName authority="Cutrim et al." authorityName="Cutrim" box="[1220,1437,1888,1910]" class="Insecta" family="Ptiloneuridae" genus="Loneura" kingdom="Animalia" order="Psocodea" pageId="1" pageNumber="254" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="duckei">
<emphasis box="[1220,1309,1888,1909]" italics="true" pageId="1" pageNumber="254">L. duckei</emphasis>
Cutrim 
<emphasis box="[1388,1437,1888,1909]" italics="true" pageId="1" pageNumber="254">et al.</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
</keyLead>
</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="1.[151,1437,1624,2027]" pageId="1" pageNumber="254">
<keyLead pageId="1" pageNumber="254">
- Posterior projections of the hypandrium widely separated, projected from the postero-lateral corners, distally curved inward, without deep median incision (see 
<figureCitation box="[560,628,1946,1968]" captionStart="FIGURES 33–40" captionStartId="8.[151,264,1943,1967]" captionTargetBox="[169,1422,199,1911]" captionTargetId="figure-25@8.[166,1422,181,1920]" captionTargetPageId="8" captionText="FIGURES 33–40. Loneura maracaensis García Aldrete (Holotype male). 33. Front view of head. 34. Left forewing. 35. Right forewing. 36. Left hindwing. 37. Right hindwing. 38. Fore- leg. 39. Mid- leg. 40. Hind- leg. Scales in mm." figureDoi="http://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.6831847" httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/6831847/files/figure.png" pageId="1" pageNumber="254">
Fig. 
<quantity box="[604,628,1946,1967]" metricMagnitude="-1" metricUnit="m" metricValue="8.382" pageId="1" pageNumber="254" unit="in" value="33.0">33</quantity>
</figureCitation>
in 
<bibRefCitation author="Cutrim, M. &amp; Silva-Neto, A. M. &amp; Garcia Aldrete, A. N. &amp; Rafael, J. A." box="[658,853,1946,1968]" pageId="1" pageNumber="254" pagination="487 - 502" refId="ref9457" refString="Cutrim, M., Silva-Neto, A. M., Garcia Aldrete, A. N. &amp; Rafael, J. A. (2021 b) Identification key, checklist and new species of Loneura Navas (Psocodea: ' Psocoptera': Ptiloneuridae) from Brazil. Zootaxa, 5057 (4), 487 - 502. https: // doi. org / 10.11646 / zootaxa. 5057.4.2" type="journal article" year="2021">
Cutrim 
<emphasis box="[732,781,1946,1968]" italics="true" pageId="1" pageNumber="254">et al.</emphasis>
, 2021b
</bibRefCitation>
)............................... 
<taxonomicName authority="(New)" baseAuthorityName="New" baseAuthorityYear="1980" box="[1240,1437,1946,1968]" class="Insecta" family="Ptiloneuridae" genus="Loneura" kingdom="Animalia" order="Psocodea" pageId="1" pageNumber="254" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="amazonica">
<emphasis box="[1240,1369,1947,1968]" italics="true" pageId="1" pageNumber="254">L. amazonica</emphasis>
(New)
</taxonomicName>
</keyLead>
</paragraph>
</keyStep>
<keyStep lastPageId="2" lastPageNumber="255" pageId="1" pageNumber="254">
<paragraph blockId="1.[151,1437,1624,2027]" pageId="1" pageNumber="254">
<keyLead pageId="1" pageNumber="254">
4. Central sclerite of the hypandrium with two posterior projections, with pointed apices (
<figureCitation box="[1062,1131,1976,1998]" captionStart="FIGURES 41–46" captionStartId="9.[151,264,1906,1930]" captionTargetBox="[195,1386,195,1865]" captionTargetId="figure-19@9.[191,1396,181,1882]" captionTargetPageId="9" captionText="FIGURES 41–46. Loneura maracaensis García Aldrete (Holotype male). 41. Phallosome (image). 42. Phallosome (drawing). 43. Hypandrium (image). 44. Hypandrium (drawing). 45. Clunium, epiproct and right and left paraprocts (image). 46. Left paraproct and (drawing). Abbreviations: aes, anterior endophallic sclerites; ep, external parameres; ms, mesal sclerite; les, lateral endophallic sclerite; pes, posterior endophallic sclerites; st, side strut. Scales in mm." figureDoi="http://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.6831849" httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/6831849/files/figure.png" pageId="1" pageNumber="254">Fig. 44</figureCitation>
)................................................................................................... 
<taxonomicName authority="Garcia Aldrete" authorityName="Garcia Aldrete" box="[1143,1436,2005,2027]" class="Insecta" family="Ptiloneuridae" genus="Loneura" kingdom="Animalia" order="Psocodea" pageId="1" pageNumber="254" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="maracaensis">
<emphasis box="[1143,1289,2006,2027]" italics="true" pageId="1" pageNumber="254">L. maracaensis</emphasis>
García Aldrete
</taxonomicName>
</keyLead>
</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="2.[151,1437,151,467]" box="[151,1436,151,173]" pageId="2" pageNumber="255">
<keyLead box="[151,1436,151,173]" pageId="2" pageNumber="255">- Central sclerite of the hypandrium with more than two posterior projections....................................... 5</keyLead>
</paragraph>
</keyStep>
<keyStep pageId="2" pageNumber="255">
<paragraph blockId="2.[151,1437,151,467]" box="[151,1436,181,203]" pageId="2" pageNumber="255">
<keyLead box="[151,1436,181,203]" pageId="2" pageNumber="255">5. Central sclerite of the hypandrium with three posterior projections............................................... 6</keyLead>
</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="2.[151,1437,151,467]" pageId="2" pageNumber="255">
